# Allow-list: only what the Go build (COPY . in docker/Dockerfile) needs.
# Everything else — .git history, .maestro control-plane state, audit
# reports, untracked local files — stays out of the build context and image
# layers (a later `rm -rf` cannot remove content from the COPY layer).
# NOTE: templates/**/*.md are embedded via go:embed and must stay included.
**
!go.mod
!go.sum
!cmd/**
!internal/**
!templates/**
!docker/entrypoint.sh
!Makefile
